    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone who prioritizes function over perfection. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings on the passenger doors, and some clear coat fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics and climate controls remain fully operational. Mechanically, it runs well, though it may soon require routine maintenance items like new brake pads or tires. It is an honest, high-mileage car that still has plenty of life left for the right owner.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience perfection with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, meticulously maintained and looking as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Every detail is flawless, from the gleaming exterior to the immaculate interior, making it a rare find for a discerning collector or anyone who appreciates the very best. This is a truly exceptional car that needs absolutely nothing.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
